{"tid":1400351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳商場一覽","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:10:03.000Z","uid":174218,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"45f1ea688b5d76f162a360063c7e87fcc10a90c0","tid":1400351,"uid":174218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"相信好少人會特登入黎將軍澳行街，作為一個二十幾年嘅將軍澳區街坊，為咗振興將軍澳經濟，為大家簡單介紹下寶琳地型，方便大家入黎行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個將軍澳可以分成五part，包括寶琳，坑口，將軍澳，調景嶺同日出康城。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN4Af8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN4Af8J.png&h=17b1168c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撇除聽日絕對唔建議任何人入嘅日出康城唔講，主要嘅購物中心會集中於寶琳，坑口同將軍澳。<br />\n<br />\n成個將軍澳嘅商場有個大共同點，就係每個站嘅商場都係相連，所以好容易會係商場入面蕩失路。<br />\n<br />\n寶琳<br />\n先講起點寶翠公園所在嘅寶琳。寶琳站由三個商場連成，分別為新都城一期 (MCP1)，二期(MCP CENTRAL)，三期(MCP DISCOVERY)。當中最大為新都城二期。而不得不提嘅係二期隔離就係將軍澳警署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3wKTVv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3wKTVv.png&h=abe59787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新都城由恒基兆業地產管理。<br />\n二同三期原本有黃阿瑪的後宮生活展覽，商場已於今日將所有展覽完全清除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMrnO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMrnO7.png&h=9b3f5ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，商場對上就係住宅。二期其中一面對住將軍澳警署，所以對上嘅住宅平台可以直接望到將軍澳警署。管理處已於三日前將住宅平台上直接對住警署嘅public area封閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfRSiny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfRSiny.png&h=54751c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通方面，除咗9鐵，相信大部分平日行經寶琳嘅巴士同小巴都會暫停或改道。最壞情況下，可以沿寶琳北路行上翠林村，有巴士可出旺角(95)，觀塘(95M)，小巴可出藍田(17)。<br />\n<br />\n其他地方有待將軍澳巴絲補充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bqcipq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bqcipq.png&h=43e57d64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqyEHQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqyEHQ6.png&h=f15a287c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望聽日夢中可以見到每一位同我一齊瘋狂購物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e59be54e561242c6ed01e83a675a0135a9f81","tid":1400351,"uid":174218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bf7b7dcb88cce837ebf6ce75b7c1e49f869d74","tid":1400351,"uid":174218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"8月4號東西夾擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be8356618b9afd99ea8c6e87080e5c52d2aa8e5","tid":1400351,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8月5 一齊罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊支持下<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"61f85885d1ddd300703efc48c8f846133c23e02e","tid":1400351,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"【小妹文宣】香港人，為咗呢個家你可以去到幾盡?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400345</a>"},{"pid":"666e5e01bec8db3636782ef8bace36546e6f52ab","tid":1400351,"uid":174218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"就算得我